debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: I was asked to click F if the number was greater than 153 and D if it was less, and I was asked to click J if the letter was closer to Z and H if it was closer to A. I was also shown shapes that were supposed to influence me to pick a letter or number based on how fast I responded and what I associated them with.

debrief.itemText: Was there any part of the experiment that you found to be confusing?
Please explain anything you found confusing. (if No, type ‘No’)
debrief.response: I never found a pattern with the shapes so I did not really understand the point.

debrief.itemText: How hard did you try during the experiment?
To what degree was your behavior influenced by the colored shapes?
Do you have any final comments on the experiment? (If no, just type No)
